Dialogue.2: You drop your line into the water, quickly drifting off into your own thoughts as you wait for a bite...
Dialogue.3: The water is quiet, as are the docks. You cast your mind back through the past few days, floating through memories of everything you've done.
Dialogue.4: Everywhere you've been, everyone you've met.
Dialogue.5: It's nice to have a moment to youself, you realize.
